Mac-Windows-VS-Mappings

eclipse\spring shortcuts

-----------------------------------

mac to windows key mapings

f1-f12 keys --> settings turn on use of function keys
backspace -->delete
delete --> fn+delete
alt -->option
control-->command
ctrl+alt+delete -->

----------------------------------------------
visual studio shortcut keys

ctrl+k -multiline comment
ctrl+shift+k -multiline  uncomment

or

ctrl+shift+k -multiline  comment
ctrl+shift+u -multiline uncomment

ctrl+. -import namespace
ctrl+, -goto dialog


ctrl+??? create a new class file from new instance
ctrl+??? add a new class method base on a method call

F5 -build
F6 -debug

right click on\in action to do add view
right click in controller to do add action ???

type class tab tab -class macro expansion
type ctor tab tab - constructor macro expansion
type prop tab tab -get set property macro expansion
